"'''Imperial Officers Field Guide'''" is an article in [[Star Wars Insider 96|''Star Wars Insider'' 96]] by [[Jonathan Wilkins]]. It is meant to be a sneak peek at the in-universe guidebook issued to [[Imperial officer/Legends|Imperial officers]] to help them adjust to life in the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]].

